<p>This is a function I made which is supposed to convert every <code>Br</code> line break into a <code>\n</code>:</p>  <pre><code>function br2nl($st){     return preg_replace('/&lt;br(\s+)?\/?&gt;/i', "\n", $st); } </code></pre>  <p>However, the output is like this:</p>  <pre><code>foo  bar  nuts </code></pre>  <p>I want it to output something like:</p>  <pre><code>foo &lt;br&gt; bar &lt;br&gt; nuts </code></pre>